<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.6.1">
<l>naṇṇāta vāḷavuṇa riṭaippukku vāṉavaraip</l>
<l>peṇṇāki yamutūṭṭum perumāṉār maruviṉiya</l>
<l>taṇṇārnta kaṭaṉmallait talacayaṉat tuṟaivārai</l>
<l>yeṇṇātē yiruppārai yiṟaippoḻutu meṇṇōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We will not think for even a second of those who exist without thinking</l>
<l>Of the one who dwells in Talacayaṉam at Mallai by the outspread sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">sweet and cool,</l>
<l>Where appears the great lord who, as a woman having entered</l>
<l>Into the midst of the hostile, cruel demons, fed nectar to the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
